{"tid":2443311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"WSJ: 歐盟本月下旬將就新疆問題制裁中國","createTime":"2021-03-12T03:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T07:11:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8aebbd44a4b6784b6acf49da8c32d3f81724f1d4","tid":2443311,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"根據《華爾街日報》，歐盟27國官員昨晚（11日）開會，同意就新疆問題制裁中國，涉及4人和1個組織，將是1989年天安門民運後，歐盟32年來首度制裁中國。有關決定將在3月22日27國外長會議正式拍板，確切被制裁名單屆時才會知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/03/blog-post_12.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F03%2Fblog-post_12.html%3Fm%3D1&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgwz2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=aaf91ef9\" target=\"_blank\">http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/03/blog-post_12.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"ec432583f6749dbed2dc358011c23211a5b79ac8","tid":2443311,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc72a098c9b0c7846d6eb293120f99900e38ceab","tid":2443311,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T03:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7edce7f7456289093c50d302e2c7342511a6148","tid":2443311,"uid":41873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"個組織係咪共產黨?<img src